{"tid":1799223,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"給最愛既前度","createTime":"2019-12-26T19:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T07:42:21.000Z","uid":248534,"like":11,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad340ce52d37828bc2a96c8d98867e51ecee485d","tid":1799223,"uid":248534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:34:20.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂呀<br />\n話咁快我地已經分開左年半<br />\n最近你po ig 坐你對面個位係你既新歡嗎？<br />\n佢畫比你個張聖誕卡都幾靚呀<br />\n睇得出你收到都好開心<br />\n我好掛住你 依句說話由暗戀你、到拍拖、直到依加 <br />\n每日都係心裡面講左唔至一次<br />\n前2年聖誕節我地既合照我重放緊係書枱上面<br />\n我知道我地已經冇可能<br />\n亦都冇勇氣去追返你<br />\n我會好好學習點放低你<br />\n希望你下一位比我更加懂得珍惜你<br />\n祝你幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391c6bac39fa88e2a5e6d29553d6a3d631a7cccb","tid":1799223,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd34e63ae425ca44d6c244331ae35ddafa21564","tid":1799223,"uid":248534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:40:12.000Z","msg":"邊個偷偷地比左負皮我又唔出聲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf272eb6641317d332b6b505f982ff3776ec7e9","tid":1799223,"uid":248534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"391c6bac39fa88e2a5e6d29553d6a3d631a7cccb","tid":1799223,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:40:36.000Z","msg":"Hi同路人"},{"pid":"176559e3a48b1727c6373c47fdf255b1dedde4b5","tid":1799223,"uid":168444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:41:23.000Z","msg":"咁鍾意人點解分手"},{"pid":"0eb9099e0637d272996619a27df117fb1251e43f","tid":1799223,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf272eb6641317d332b6b505f982ff3776ec7e9","tid":1799223,"uid":248534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"